title: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
headline: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
content:
Thank you for being a GTA+ Member. Don’t forget to claim all of your GTA+ benefits by May 28:

— The Mammoth Mil-Spec (Off-Road)
— 50% off Agency Properties
— 2X GTA$ and RP on Payphone Hits
— 2X GTA$ on Garment Factory income
— 50% off Imani Tech Upgrades
— The Bigness Sketches Shirt and Jeans
— And more

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
